---
title: Prosciutto-Loaded Toasts with Goat Cheese, Rocket & Beetroot Relish
description: Add a touch of holiday magic to your gathering with these festive nibbles! Topped with creamy goat cheese, peppery rocket, and a sweet beetroot relish, every bite is a celebration of summery flavours. Perfect as a merry starter or a holiday snack, these toasts are sure to bring some extra cheer to your festive spread!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
